| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-4338 — Mass File Rename (hunters)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 87ca9310-798d-588b-84a8-9e7f908fff15"
index=*
| where (file_path="*.encrypted" OR file_path="*.locked" OR file_path="*.ransom")
